id: pm-f2al
title: "ADR: offline BM25 lexical provider + relevance eval harness for search quality"
description: ""
type: Decision
status: open
priority: 2
tags[3]: adr,"area:search","area:semantic"
created_at: "2026-06-20T05:29:45.329Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-20T05:29:45.329Z"
